org.spongepowered.api

Class CatalogTypes

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.spongepowered.api.CatalogTypes

  • public final class CatalogTypes
extends Object
    Enumeration of all known CatalogTypes for autocompletion when using the GameRegistry to retrieve specific types or all of a certain type.

    These are generally useful for GameRegistry.getType(Class, String) and GameRegistry.getAllOf(Class).
